The WastelandsAres12/31/3037You are being sent to the enemy'sdetention facility at the outskirts oftheir domain, a place of torture andslavery for those unlucky enough to be"guests" of the regime.You have 2 targets:A) Preliminary TargetDestroy the radar installation to knockout defenses.B) Main TargetEliminate the two hangars on the runway.Intelligence reports each hangarcontains 6 short range fighters. Do notengage in combat unless you are confidentof victory.- MOTHERSHIP -Callum Blaze#